Uni-app是一个跨平台开发框架，它可以将一个应用程序打包成多种平台下的应用程序，其中包括了App-Plus平台。App-Plus是Uni-app为移动端提供的一种运行容器，它可以让开发者在一些原生功能上进行操作，比如设置底部导航栏的按钮。以下是动态设置App-Plus下的buttons的步骤。

1. 设置页面路由及底部导航栏

在Uni-app中，底部导航栏可以通过pages.json配置文件中的tabBar属性进行设置。首先需要在pages.json文件中定义页面路由，并将需要在底部导航栏展示的页面添加到tabBar.list数组中。例如：

```
"pages": [
    {
        "path": "pages/home/home",
        "name": "home",
        "style": {}
    },
    {
        "path": "pages/order/order",
        "name": "order",
        "style": {}
    }
],
"tabBar": {
    "color": "#999999",
    "selectedColor": "#007aff",
    "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
    "list": [
        {
            "pagePath": "pages/home/home",
            "text": "首页",
            "iconPath": "static/tabBar/home.png",
            "selectedIconPath": "static/tabBar/home-select.png"
        },
        {
            "pagePath": "pages/order/order",
            "text": "订单",
            "iconPath": "static/tabBar/order.png",
            "selectedIconPath": "static/tabBar/order-select.png"
        }
    ]
}
```

2. 获取底部导航栏按钮数组

在页面中，通过uni.getSystemInfoSync()方法可以获取当前运行环境的系统信息，通过system.indexOf('iOS') > -1判断是否为iOS系统，然后可以调用uni.getMenuButtonBoundingClientRect()方法获取到底部导航栏的按钮信息。最后通过tabBar.list[]数组中的索引值获取对应的按钮信息。例如：

```
const system = uni.getSystemInfoSync().system
const menuButtonInfo = uni.getMenuButtonBoundingClientRect()
if (system.indexOf('iOS') > -1) {
    // iOS系统需要向下调整10像素
    menuButtonInfo.top += 10
    menuButtonInfo.bottom += 10
}
const tabBarInfo = this.$pagesConfig.tabBar.list[this.$mp.page.$page.index]
```

3. 动态设置按钮位置和大小

获取到底部导航栏按钮的位置和大小信息后，可以通过uni.setTabBarBadge()和uni.setTabBarItem()方法来设置按钮的位置和大小属性。例如：

```
uni.setTabBarBadge({
    index: tabBarInfo.index,
    text: '123',
    success () {
        uni.setTabBarItem({
            index: tabBarInfo.index,
            iconPath: 'static/tabBar/home-select.png',
            selectedIconPath: 'static/tabBar/home-select.png',
            success () {
                uni.setTabBarItem({
                    index: tabBarInfo.index,
                    text: 'Hello',
                    success () {
                        // 设置完成
                    }
                })
            }
        })
    }
})
```

以上是动态设置App-Plus下的buttons的步骤。需要注意的是，底部导航栏按钮的位置和大小属性只能在App-Plus平台下进行设置。在H5平台下，底部导航栏的按钮是由浏览器自带的菜单栏来显示的，无法进行设置。

Yes, D3D11 has an interface to set the line width before drawing a line. The interface is called ID3D11DeviceContext and specifically, the Draw method with primitive topology set to D3D11_PRIMITIVE_TOPOLOGY_LINELIST or D3D11_PRIMITIVE_TOPOLOGY_LINESTRIP.

To set the line width, you need to create a rasterizer state object with the desired line width value and set it as the current rasterizer state before calling the Draw method. Here is an example of how to create a rasterizer state with a line width of 2.0:

```C++
D3D11_RASTERIZER_DESC rasterizerDesc = {};
rasterizerDesc.FillMode = D3D11_FILL_SOLID;
rasterizerDesc.CullMode = D3D11_CULL_NONE;
rasterizerDesc.DepthClipEnable = true;
rasterizerDesc.AntialiasedLineEnable = true;
rasterizerDesc.MultisampleEnable = true;
rasterizerDesc.ScissorEnable = false;
rasterizerDesc.SlopeScaledDepthBias = 0.0f;
rasterizerDesc.DepthBias = 0;

rasterizerDesc.FillMode = D3D11_FILL_SOLID;

// Set line width to 2.0f
rasterizerDesc.AntialiasedLineEnable = TRUE;
rasterizerDesc.MultisampleEnable = TRUE;
rasterizerDesc.DepthClipEnable = TRUE;
rasterizerDesc.CullMode = D3D11_CULL_BACK;

rasterizerDesc.FrontCounterClockwise = false;
rasterizerDesc.ScissorEnable = false;
rasterizerDesc.SlopeScaledDepthBias = 0.0f;
rasterizerDesc.DepthBias = 0;

ID3D11RasterizerState* rasterizerState;
device->CreateRasterizerState(&rasterizerDesc, &rasterizerState);

// Set the rasterizer state with the desired line width value
deviceContext->RSSetState(rasterizerState);

// Draw the line(s)
deviceContext->Draw(lineCount, vertexOffset);
```

