- The `glObjectLabel` function reference: https://www.khronos.org/registry/OpenGL-Refpages/gl4/html/glObjectLabel.xhtml

- The `glPushDebugGroup` and `glPopDebugGroup` function references: https://www.khronos.org/registry/OpenGL-Refpages/gl4/html/glPushDebugGroup.xhtml, https://www.khronos.org/registry/OpenGL-Refpages

